<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Quarterly Review — {{ dev_name }} — {{ quarter_label }}</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif;
         background: #f8f8fb; color: #222; padding: 48px; max-width: 820px;
         margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; }
  h1 { font-size: 26px; color: #111; margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .sub { color: #666; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 14px; }
  h2 { font-size: 15px; color: #222; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 10px;
       border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 6px; text-transform: uppercase;
       letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-weight: 600; }
  .score-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 8px 0;
               border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; font-size: 14px; }
  .score-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .score-row strong { color: #111; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .highlight { background: #fff8e1; padding: 16px 20px; border-left: 4px solid #ffaa00;
               border-radius: 4px; margin: 16px 0; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
  p { margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
  .strength-item, .growth-item { padding: 6px 0 6px 18px; position: relative; }
  .strength-item::before, .growth-item::before {
    content: "•"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #ffaa00; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .trend-rising { color: #0ea572; }
  .trend-declining { color: #c94545; }
  .trend-flat { color: #888; }
  .footer { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 11px; color: #888; }
  @media print {
    body { padding: 24px; }
    .highlight { break-inside: avoid; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Quarterly Review — {{ dev_name }}</h1>
<div class="sub">{{ quarter_label }} · Generated {{ generated_at }}</div>

<h2>Summary</h2>
<p>{{ summary_paragraph }}</p>

<h2>13-week merit trend</h2>
<div class="score-row"><span>Average merit score</span><strong>{{ avg_merit }}/100</strong></div>
<div class="score-row"><span>Trend</span><strong class="trend-{{ trend | lower }}">{{ trend | capitalize }}</strong></div>
<div class="score-row"><span>Consecutive green weeks (streak)</span><strong>{{ green_weeks }}</strong></div>

<h2>Contribution totals (over 13 weeks)</h2>
<div class="score-row"><span>Items closed</span><strong>{{ total_items_closed }}</strong></div>
<div class="score-row"><span>Off-project hours logged</span><strong>{{ total_off_project }}h</strong></div>
<div class="score-row"><span>Blockers cleared for other devs</span><strong>{{ total_unblocks }}</strong></div>
<div class="score-row"><span>QA bugs caused (reducing Quality signal)</span><strong>{{ qa_bugs_caused }}</strong></div>

<h2>Strengths observed</h2>
{% for s in strengths %}<div class="strength-item">{{ s }}</div>{% endfor %}

<h2>Growth areas</h2>
{% for g in growth_areas %}<div class="growth-item">{{ g }}</div>{% endfor %}

<h2>Recommendation</h2>
<div class="highlight">{{ recommendation }}</div>

<div class="footer">
  Review generated by devdash on {{ generated_at }}. Merit score derived from six
  weighted signals: Output, Quality, Reliability, Handoff discipline, Initiative, and
  Unblock factor. Fahad reviews and edits this draft before delivery.
</div>

</body>
</html>
